PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776935153
OL,3,CUK agrees new #500 million deal with
OL,4,CFrance to tackle migrant crossings
OL,6,FA new deal with France aimed at
OL,7,Freducing the number of small boat
OL,8,Fcrossings has been announced by Home
OL,9,FSecretary Shabana Mahmood.
OL,11,FThe deal, which pays France to patrol
OL,12,Fits beaches and stop migrant
OL,13,Fcrossings, will see an expansion of
OL,14,Flaw enforcement deployed across
OL,15,FNorthern France.
OL,17,FIn exchange, the UK will pay France
OL,18,F#500 million, with a further #160
OL,19,Fmillion contingent on results.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
