FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776935153
OL,3,CUK agrees new #500 million deal with
OL,4,CFrance to tackle migrant crossings
OL,6,FITV News explains what is included in
OL,7,Fthe deal and where the money is being
OL,8,Fspent.
OL,10,FWhat is included in the deal?
OL,12,FThe new deal will see an increase in
OL,13,Flaw enforcement officials, the
OL,14,Fdeployment of a new unit of specially
OL,15,Ftrained officers, and an expansion of
OL,16,Fseveral units already in operation.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776935153
OL,3,CUK agrees new #500 million deal with
OL,4,CFrance to tackle migrant crossings
OL,6,FCurrently, around 750 law enforcement
OL,7,Fpersonnel are deployed to French
OL,8,Fbeaches, who have stopped 42,000
OL,9,Fattempted crossings to Britain since
OL,10,FLabour took office. Across several
OL,11,Fdistinct units, this number is set to
OL,12,Frise by 40%.
OL,14,FThis will include a new unit of 50
OL,15,Fpolice officers specially trained in
OL,16,Friot and crowd control tactics, and
OL,17,Fequipment to deal with hostile crowds
OL,18,Fand violent tactics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776935153
OL,3,CUK agrees new #500 million deal with
OL,4,CFrance to tackle migrant crossings
OL,6,FThe intelligence and judicial police
OL,7,Funit of 18 people is set to expand to
OL,8,F30, in an effort to increase the
OL,9,Farrest rate and prosecution of people
OL,10,Fsmugglers across the region.
OL,12,FDrone surveillance, two new
OL,13,Fhelicopters, and a new camera system
OL,14,Fwill also be deployed to assist law
OL,15,Fenforcement officers in their
OL,16,Foperations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776935153
OL,3,CUK agrees new #500 million deal with
OL,4,CFrance to tackle migrant crossings
OL,6,FFrench officials will also increase
OL,7,Fthe targeting of so-called taxi boats
OL,8,F- where people smugglers try to avoid
OL,9,Fdetection by sending one person
OL,10,Fsailing a dinghy along the coast alone
OL,11,Fto beaches where migrants scramble
OL,12,Faboard in the water.
OL,14,FHow much will it cost?
OL,16,FThe new deal will cost the UK #500
OL,17,Fmillion, with an extra #160 million
OL,18,Fpledged depending on performance.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
