FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776935153
OL,3,CUK agrees new #500 million deal with
OL,4,CFrance to tackle migrant crossings
OL,6,FThis is up from the #478 million the
OL,7,FConservatives committed to the
OL,8,Fprevious deal in 2023.
OL,10,FThat deal expired last month, with the
OL,11,Fhome secretary signing a last-minute
OL,12,F#16.2 million stopgap arrangement
OL,13,Fwhile negotiations continued.
OL,15,FThe Home Office told ITV News this
OL,16,Fagreement would be in place for three
OL,17,Fyears and that the additional #160
OL,18,Fmillion would be redirected if the
OL,19,Fwork carried out by law officials was
OL,20,Fdeemed unsuccessful.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776935153
OL,3,CUK agrees new #500 million deal with
OL,4,CFrance to tackle migrant crossings
OL,6,FThe Home Office said it would not put
OL,7,Fa target on the number of small boat
OL,8,Finterceptions.
OL,10,FJoint work with the French has stopped
OL,11,Fover 42,000 illegal migrants
OL,12,Fattempting to cross the channel
OL,13,Fthrough intervention and dispersal.
OL,14,FJoint law enforcement operations have
OL,15,Falso seen 480 migrant traffickers
OL,16,Farrested in 2025.
OL,18,FWhat have UK officials said?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
