FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776935153
OL,3,CUK agrees new #500 million deal with
OL,4,CFrance to tackle migrant crossings
OL,6,FAnnouncing the deal, Home Secretary
OL,7,FShabana Mahmood said: "Our work with
OL,8,Fthe French has stopped tens of
OL,9,Fthousands of illegal migrants boarding
OL,10,Fboats headed to Britain.
OL,12,F"But we must do more. This landmark
OL,13,Fdeal will stop illegal migrants making
OL,14,Fthe perilous journey and put people
OL,15,Fsmugglers behind bars."
OL,26,@oD@WOUtD@AOUwD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776935153
OL,3,CUK agrees new #500 million deal with
OL,4,CFrance to tackle migrant crossings
OL,6,FHailing the new agreement, the prime
OL,7,Fminister said: "We must restore order
OL,8,Fand control to our borders. That means
OL,9,Fbearing down on these dangerous
OL,10,Fcrossings and bringing people
OL,11,Fsmugglers to justice.
OL,13,F"This historic agreement means we can
OL,14,Fgo further: ramping up intelligence,
OL,15,Fsurveillance and boots on the ground
OL,16,Fto protect Britain's borders."
OL,18,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
