OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776935153
OL,3,CUK agrees new #500 million deal with
OL,4,CFrance to tackle migrant crossings
OL,6,FDoes anyone oppose the bill?
OL,8,FSome argue that a focus on small boat
OL,9,Fcrossings does little to treat the
OL,10,Fcause of the issue.
OL,12,FImran Hussain, Director of External
OL,13,FAffairs at Refugee Council, accused
OL,14,Fthe government of "treating the
OL,15,Fsymptom not the cause", saying that
OL,16,Fpolicing alone won't "prevent
OL,17,Fdesperate people" from turning to
OL,18,Fsmall boats.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776935153
OL,3,CUK agrees new #500 million deal with
OL,4,CFrance to tackle migrant crossings
OL,6,F"We know from our frontline services
OL,7,Fwhy people risk their lives to reach
OL,8,Fthe UK: many already speak some
OL,9,FEnglish, have family here, or have
OL,10,Fcultural connections to Britain," he
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"After fleeing brutal persecution and
OL,14,Fwar in countries like Afghanistan and
OL,15,FSudan, they just want to rebuild their
OL,16,Flives in peace. But the government has
OL,17,Fshut down the few safe and legal
OL,18,Fpathways available, including family
OL,19,Freunion, a route that overwhelmingly
OL,20,Fhelped women and children," he added.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776935153
OL,3,CUK agrees new #500 million deal with
OL,4,CFrance to tackle migrant crossings
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the Conservatives argue
OL,7,Fthis is money poorly spent.
OL,9,FShadow Home Secretary Chris Philp
OL,10,Fsaid: "The government's deal hands
OL,11,Fover half a billion pounds of our
OL,12,Fmoney with no conditions at all.
OL,13,FFrance only prevented a third of
OL,14,Fembarkations last year and even let
OL,15,Fthose illegal immigrants go to try
OL,16,Fagain. France shouldn't get a single
OL,17,Fpenny unless they stop the vast
OL,18,Fmajority of the boats.
OL,26,@rD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1776935153
OL,3,CUK agrees new #500 million deal with
OL,4,CFrance to tackle migrant crossings
OL,6,F"This weak government has no control
OL,7,Fof our borders. Since the election,
OL,8,Fover 70,000 illegal immigrants have
OL,9,Fcrossed ` a 45 per cent increase
OL,10,Fcompared to before the election. Their
OL,11,Fclaim to smash the gangs is laughable.
OL,13,F"The only way to fix this is the
OL,14,FConservative Party's Borders plan `
OL,15,Fleave the ECHR so we can deport all
OL,16,Fillegal immigrants within a week of
OL,17,Farrival, and then the crossings would
OL,18,Fsoon stop. But Shabana Mahmood and
OL,19,FKeir Starmer are too weak to do this."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
